00:09:27.699 --> 00:09:32.559
lifespan is all more amazing as it was
only ever built to last for three months.

00:09:32.559 --> 00:09:38.559
Its twin the Spirit rover lasted over
six years before being stuck in a sand

00:09:38.559 --> 00:09:43.119
trap which limited its ability to
recharge its battery and led to his

00:09:43.119 --> 00:09:50.170
eventual demise in 2007. The Curiosity
rover landed in 2012 and was expected to

00:09:50.170 --> 00:09:54.699
last for two years but has been active
now for 6-1/2  years and its

