to function which could be many years
from now barring an unexpected event. But

00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:09.730
the longest-lived craft are those which
we have sent to the farthest planets and

00:10:09.730 --> 00:10:13.360
beyond. Currently there are five such spacecraft

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:20.259
pioneer 10 and 11 Voyager 1 and 2 and
New Horizons. There are also some of the

00:10:20.259 --> 00:10:24.759
